title: Watts Beauty ArganGoldTM 120ml /100% Cert. Organic Cold Pressed Argan Nut Oil - Hair & Body -Morocco
description: Yes, this is the popular Watts Beauty product that everyone is searching for. Don't buy a whole new line of products, simply add a few drops of this pure argan oil to your favorite hair and skin products to enhance their results and benefits. Watts Beauty Argan Gold is produced by a women's cooperative that shares the profits among the local women of the Berber tribe.
